# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# AgentStreams .gitattributes — Memory Palace + Linguist Overrides
# Inspired by milla-jovovich/mempalace architecture
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── Line Ending Normalization ────────────────────────────────
* text=auto

# Python: always LF
*.py text eol=lf
*.pyi text eol=lf

# Shell scripts: always LF
*.sh text eol=lf
*.bash text eol=lf

# Markdown / TTL / SQL: always LF
*.md text eol=lf
*.ttl text eol=lf
*.sql text eol=lf

# TypeScript / JavaScript / JSX
*.ts text eol=lf
*.tsx text eol=lf
*.js text eol=lf
*.jsx text eol=lf
*.mjs text eol=lf
*.css text eol=lf

# Config files
*.toml text eol=lf
*.yaml text eol=lf
*.yml text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.graphqls text eol=lf
*.avsc text eol=lf

# ── Linguist Overrides (GitHub language detection) ───────────
# Mark generated projections as generated (excluded from stats)
ontology/projections/** linguist-generated=true

# Mark vendor research as vendored (excluded from stats)
vendors/** linguist-vendored=true

# Mark taxonomy crawl output as generated
taxonomy/** linguist-generated=true

# Lock files are generated
uv.lock linguist-generated=true
webapp/package-lock.json linguist-generated=true
skills-lock.json linguist-generated=true

# ── Memory Palace Wings ─────────────────────────────────────
# Following mempalace architecture: wings (domains), rooms (topics),
# halls (memory types), tunnels (cross-wing connections)
# Ref: milla-jovovich/mempalace — verbatim storage, vector retrieval
#
# Wing: ontology/     — UDA source of truth (TTL, SQL, mappings)
# Wing: src/          — Programmatic tools (bloom, crawlers, dspy, mcp)
# Wing: scripts/      — CLI crawlers and pipeline runners
# Wing: skills/       — Multi-language skill packages
# Wing: .claude/      — Agent and subagent manifests + memory sync
# Wing: webapp/       — Next.js 16 + Tailwind + Motion landing page
# Wing: .github/      — CI/CD workflows, security rules, branch protection
# Wing: evals/        — Promptfoo evaluation suites
#
# Halls bridge wings:
#   hall_facts    → ontology/*.ttl + ontology/schema.sql
#   hall_tools    → src/*.py + scripts/*.py
#   hall_agents   → .claude/agents/*.md + .claude/subagents/*.md
#   hall_skills   → skills/*/SKILL.md + .claude/skills/*.md
#   hall_evals    → evals/*/promptfooconfig.yaml
#   hall_ci       → .github/workflows/*.yml + .github/BRANCH_PROTECTION.md
#   hall_webapp   → webapp/src/**/*.tsx + webapp/src/app/globals.css
#   hall_safety   → .github/security-instructions.txt + .github/fp-filtering.txt
#
# Tunnels (cross-wing connections):
#   ontology → src/projections.py (generates Avro/GraphQL from TTL)
#   src/bloom.py → scripts/spiders.py (bloom filter shared across wings)
#   src/crawlers.py → scripts/crawl-sitemap.py (UDACrawler replaces inline)
#   src/neon_db.py → scripts/crawl-sitemap.py (data layer replaces inline)
#   src/dspy_prompts.py → .claude/subagents/ (signatures define extraction)
#   src/orchestrator.py → .claude/agents/*.md (agent configs ↔ frontmatter)
#   .claude/agents/ → .github/workflows/agent-boundary-check.yml (CI validates)
#   .github/security-instructions.txt → .claude/agents/security-auditor.md
#   webapp/package.json → @neondatabase/serverless (Neon edge queries)
#   webapp/package.json → @anthropic-ai/claude-agent-sdk (agent runtime)
#
# SDK Ecosystem (tunnels to npm registry):
#   @anthropic-ai/claude-agent-sdk  — Agent runtime (query, hooks, subagents)
#   @anthropic-ai/claude-code       — CLI package (renamed to agent-sdk)
#   @anthropic-ai/claude-trace      — JSONL transcript capture + web UI
#   @anthropic-ai/sdk               — Direct Messages API client
#   @anthropic-ai/mcpb              — MCP Bundle builder (desktop extensions)
#   @neondatabase/serverless        — Neon SQL over HTTPS/WebSocket
#   @neondatabase/neon-js           — Neon Auth + Data API (PostgREST)
#
# Claude Code Memory Sync:
#   CLAUDE.md          — Shared project memory (checked in, all sessions)
#   CLAUDE.local.md    — Private local memory (gitignored, per-developer)
#   ~/.claude/CLAUDE.md — Global memory (cross-project preferences)
#   .claude/skills/remember.md — Memory organization skill
#   .claude/agents/memory-validator.md — Three-layer memory validation

# ── Binary Files (no diff, no merge) ────────────────────────
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.pdf binary
*.avro binary

# ── Bloom Filter State (binary persistence) ─────────────────
*.bloom binary

# ── LanceDB / Vector Store Files ─────────────────────────────
*.lance binary
*.idx binary
